mic over to you if you want to ask it live. Sure thanks for doing this Paul. Retail is pretty

00:08:03.799 --> 00:08:12.359
interesting. How do you tackle the whole data, the data along the supply chain up to the retail

00:08:12.359 --> 00:08:23.559
