00:08:23.559 --> 00:08:30.600
information? How does it work in this context? So it's a little interesting with alcohol sales in

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:36.679
America. We have what's called a three-tiered system where we're not allowed to sell directly

00:08:36.679 --> 00:08:42.599
to the store that sells it to you. This is a post-prohibition legal effect that's been in

00:08:42.599 --> 00:08:47.640
