00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:11.799
headache because you have to deal with like what we're shipping to this third party and then what

00:09:11.799 --> 00:09:16.280
they're shipping to a consumer, right? So it's like two different sets of metrics but we are

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:21.320
kind of lucky that we have we can get to that store level data. But we have a lot of creative

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:27.000
assets in play to try to get us that information as quickly and as at the lowest level possible.

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:27.799
It's not always easy.

